title: Painting Vibrant Orange
description:
Follow this step by step guide to learn how to easily paint a vibrant orange colour on your models for Warhammer Age of Sigmar and Warhammer 40,000.        

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6

title: How to Paint: Cities of Sigmar - The Living City Cloth & Shield
description:
The Living City thrives in harmony with nature, its cunning mortal defenders working alongside Sylvaneth spirit-allies. In this video, we'll show you how to quickly and easily paint the verdant colour scheme of the Living City, so you'll be able to amass a painted force that looks great on the tabletop.         

If you're new to painting - check out our Citadel Colour Painting Essentials videos to learn all about it: http://warhammer.me/3Vkojs6
